00:22:21.950 --> 00:22:28.150
as much semantics in there, but so that you or
someone else or someone with an assistive technology

00:22:28.150 --> 00:22:32.990
or search engine can get semantic data out of your page.

00:22:32.990 --> 00:22:39.240
Someone who is using assistive technology or a
