00:22:39.240 --> 00:22:42.890
they don't see your site, they only read your code.

00:22:42.890 --> 00:22:49.100
They read your markup and you want them to know well
this is a list and you want them to be able to convey

00:22:49.099 --> 00:22:55.879
that information back to the user so you
want your, the more semantic your code is,

00:22:55.880 --> 00:23:00.160
the easier it becomes for assistive
technology but also search engines

00:23:00.160 --> 00:23:06.290
