00:24:11.710 --> 00:24:17.559
Then after a while he searched for it and
what he discovered was that the more valid

00:24:17.559 --> 00:24:26.109
and the more semantically rich the pages he created
was, the higher up it was in the search results.

00:24:26.109 --> 00:24:32.549
So he discovered also that keyword placement whether it
is at the top or the bottom of the page didn't matter,

00:24:32.549 --> 00:24:39.119
